<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP6">
<l>tuṇṭa veṇpiṟai yaṉṟuyar tīrttava ṉañciṟaiya</l>
<l>vaṇṭu vāḻpoḻil cūḻaraṅ kanakar mēyavappa</l>
<l>ṉaṇṭa raṇṭa pakiraṇ ṭattoru māni lameḻu mālvarai muṟṟu</l>
<l>muṇṭa kaṇṭaṅkaṇ ṭīraṭi yēṉaiyuy yakkoṇṭatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Look, the throat—which swallowed all, the [cosmic] egg of the celestials,</l>
<l>the outer worlds, the big, unique earth, the seven chief mountain [ranges],</l>
<l>of the Father who dwells in the town of Raṅgam surrounded by groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where pretty-winged bees live,</l>
<l>of Him who destroyed the affliction of he with a sliver of the white crescent moon—</l>
<l rend="indent">took me, a servant, so that I am saved.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
